frame Grant permission to colleagues

fontawesome6solid f390 WebApp
participant API Gateway
participant Tournament Manager
participant Mail Manager

participantspacing 5

activate WebApp
WebApp->API Gateway: grantPermission(id Tournament, id Educator)
activate API Gateway
API Gateway->Tournament Manager: grantPermission(id Tournament, id Educator)
activate Tournament Manager

Tournament Manager->Mail Manager: sendEmail(id Educator, content)
activate Mail Manager
Mail Manager-->Tournament Manager: result
deactivate Mail Manager
Tournament Manager-->API Gateway: result
deactivate Tournament Manager

API Gateway-->WebApp: result
deactivate WebApp
deactivate API Gateway

